snippet.textDisplay: First Death in HK, 39 years old male. He went to Wuhan on 21 JAN, came back to HK on 23 JAN, started to have muscle pain on 29 JAN, had fever on 31 JAN and sent to the hospital, 4th FED dead. 5 Nurses who treated that patient start to have fever and diarrhea, all 5 nurse are on isolation.
